{
  "chapter": 36,
  "chapter_summary": "沈浪发现快活王招揽的新英雄竟是熊猫儿，二人在暴雨中把臂重逢，互诉衷肠。沈浪向熊猫儿倾吐了与快活王势不两立的秘密原因，以及为除快活王不惜与王家母子合作的决心。然而熊猫儿突然出手点穴，原来此人竟是龙四海假扮——快活王为试探沈浪真心，命龙四海易容成熊猫儿模样。龙四海透露真正的熊猫儿已被独孤伤杀害。与此同时，王怜花趁沈浪不在，强行与染香亲热后告知她朱七七已嫁给自己。沈浪身陷绝境，独孤伤突然出现阻止龙四海动手，表示要亲自动手杀沈浪。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "但望王爷相告。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦……此人是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "此人自也是天下之英雄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人现在何处？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "猫儿，你又醉了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "醉，谁醉了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我熊猫儿会是泄露机密的人么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自然不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "你说的她，可是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然是那王……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "她行事竟能出你意料，自然是个好角色。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她可当真为朱七七与王怜花订了婚事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人，女人……简直都不是东西。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱七七真的心甘情愿？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见鬼的才懂得女人的心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "但她也该知道你此举别有用意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "你既觉如此痛苦，为何不放下那副担子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然，这其中有个原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那又是什么原因？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "莫非你与快活王有什么私人的恩怨不成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是为了白飞飞？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想我会是为了她么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那又是为了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是我心底的秘密，我现在还不能说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "你何时才能说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "等快活王死的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "他不会比你先死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "你不是熊猫儿。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "熊猫儿",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_long_si_hai",
      "text": "你……你莫非是龙四海？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "熊猫儿",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "你为何不早些想到？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，任何人都会上人当的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "但咱们为了要你上当，的确也花了不少心思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但还有……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有声音，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "但熊猫儿他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "text": "快活王莫非怀疑了他，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "快活王倒未怀疑他，怀疑的是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一试之下，你果然露了原形。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如今你又想怎样？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好，不想我沈浪今日竟死在这里。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "不想声名赫赫的沈浪今日竟死在我手里。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只想再问你一句话。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "你还有什么话好问？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "text": "我只要知道，熊猫儿此刻在哪里？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "好，你和熊猫儿果然不愧为生死共命的交情，直到此时此刻，你还是忘不了他，好，我告诉你……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他……他也遭了毒手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是……是谁下的毒手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "沈……沈浪？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "text": "公子……是你。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小鬼，总算被你猜着了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼要你这样补偿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不想？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想，不想，偏不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非这两天沈浪已喂饱了你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人家才不像你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就知道他是个正人君子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在不是问话的时候，是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪，他……他此刻会回来么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是独孤兄。那猫儿已解决了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "那沈浪还等什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不能杀他。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": "char_shen_lang",
      "text": "要杀沈浪，只有某家亲自动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "龙四海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，请。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在有个人还在等着我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你永远想不到她是谁的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱七七。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱七七？她也来了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然。告诉你，她已嫁给了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嫁……嫁给了你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "享受……享受……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这恶魔……恶鬼……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ran_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "染香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "骚婆娘，你怕我以后不来找你了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想要的时候，还是要来的……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是荡妇……我真是荡妇么？沈浪……沈浪，你也说我是荡妇么……沈浪，沈浪，你为什么还不回来看看我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    }
